      </a>
      <a class="card" href="#">
        <div class="card-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497486751825-1233686d5d80?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"><span class="card-pill badge badge-light">Blog</span></div>
